      • outcome

        public String outcome()
        retrieve textual information on the outcome of this corona-test.
        There are two possible outcomes, depending on the result.
        For positive tests, this method returns "positive, quarantine till:" and the date until which the result of this corona-test is considered valid.
        For negative tests, this method returns "negative, valid till:" and the date until which the result of this corona-test is considered valid.
        Returns:
        the textual information on the outcome
